    / START STORY SECTION
    %section#story
      .row
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-sm-offset-3.intro
          %h1 A few of our stories
          %p "It began almost 20 years ago, in a small living room near the centre of town. Now, the church is all over the city and beyond."
          %p "I was an emotional wreck before coming back to church. They call this church the church of the second chance (and the third, and the fourth...!) and I've definitely experienced that first hand."
          %p "We don't just exist for the members. Following Jesus is supposed to be about loving your city and neighbourhood, and we're trying to do that as best we can."
          %p "Deep down, I never thought God actually intervened in people's lives: I figured he was far off and disinterested. That is, until I prayed for someone's back pain to go... and it did."
          %p "You should come along and check it out on a Sunday. It's worth seeing for yourself whether God is actually real. Don't just believe what other people say!"
      .studio
        .row
          .col-xs-12
            #swiper.swiper-container
              .swiper-wrapper
                .swiper-slide
                  %img{:alt => "slider image 1", :src => "http://placehold.it/960x540/999999/1a1a1a&amp;text=960x540"}/
                .swiper-slide
                  %img{:alt => "slider image 2", :src => "http://placehold.it/960x540//1a1a1a/999999&amp;text=Best+with+aspect+ratio+16:9"}/
                .swiper-slide
