    / END STUDIO SECTION
    / START SUNDAYS SECTION
    %section#sundays
      .row
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-sm-offset-3.intro
          %h1 Sunday
          %p
            "The church meets each Sunday morning. Things kick off around 10:30, but most people show up early to get coffee."
          %p
            %a{:href => '#contact'} Find out how to get to the meeting &raquo;
          %p
            "The kids groups start from about 10:20 or so. They've got wonderful leaders who pray with them, sing with them and do loads of crafts and activites."
      #services-list.container.row
        .col-xs-3.col-sm-6.col-md-3
          #worship.service.smooth
            %i.icon-music.icon-4x
            %h5.hidden-xs Worship
        .col-xs-3.col-sm-6.col-md-3
          #teaching.service.smooth
            %i.icon-book.icon-4x
            %h5.hidden-xs Teaching
        .col-xs-3.col-sm-6.col-md-3
          #praying.service.smooth
            %i.icon-cloud-download.icon-4x
            %h5.hidden-xs Praying
        .col-xs-3.col-sm-6.col-md-3
          #coffee.service.smooth
            %i.icon-coffee.icon-4x
            %h5.hidden-xs Coffee
      .container
        .row
          .col-xs-12.col-sm-12.col-md-12.col-lg-12
            #worship-skills.skills-bar
              .row
                .col-xs-12.col-sm-4.col-sm-offset-1
                  %p "We normally spend about half an hour with a band playing a few simple songs, and people sing if they want to or just sit and watch."
                .col-xs-12.col-sm-4.col-sm-offset-2
                  %p "We're connecting with God. He helps us focus on him alone and not on ourselves. It's pretty liberating."
            #teaching-skills.skills-bar
              .row
                .col-xs-12.col-sm-4.col-sm-offset-1
                  %p "Most Sundays we have 20-30 minutes of teaching based on something in the bible. It's always really practical: like a fuel injection for the soul."
                .col-xs-12.col-sm-4.col-sm-offset-2
                  %p "I think it's really important to know what's real and what isn't, otherwise we are ruled by our feelings and whims."
              %p
                %a{:href => '#news'} Latest talk downloads &raquo;
            #praying-skills.skills-bar
              .row
                .col-xs-12.col-sm-4.col-sm-offset-1
                  %p "People come in all sorts of places emotionally and spiritually. God always meets them where they're at - he's so kind and merciful."
                .col-xs-12.col-sm-4.col-sm-offset-2
                  %p "The people leading the service always make space to pray for the sick and for those who need help, and anyone challenged by the events of the morning."
            #coffee-skills.skills-bar
              .row
                .col-xs-12.col-sm-4.col-sm-offset-1
                  %p "We always make time to hang out, drink coffee, and chat after things are finished up."
                .col-xs-12.col-sm-4.col-sm-offset-2
                  %p "Usually everyone finally gets kicked out at least an hour after the official finish!"
    / END SERVICES SECTION
    / START WORKS SECTION
    %section#activity
      .row
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-sm-offset-3.intro
          %h1 Things we do
          %p "I really wanted to be a part of a church that hangs out and is active throughout the week, not just on a Sunday morning all dressed up."
          %p "There's a huge amount that goes on here: band jamming sessions, life group meetups, children's clothes giveaways, feeding the homeless on a Saturday night."
